headline: Saguaro Biosciences Partners with Bio-Techne to Distribute Innovative Live-Cell Imaging Reagents
summary: QUEBEC CITY, October 15, 2025--Saguaro Biosciences, a pioneer in non-toxic live cell reagents for enhanced drug insights, announces a new distribution agreement with Bio-Techne Corporation (NASDAQ:TECH), a global provider of life science tools, reagents and diagnostic products. The partnership will leverage Bio-Techne’s extensive international sales and marketing channels to provide researchers worldwide with better access to Saguaro’s portfolio of non-toxic, wash-free dyes.

headline: Bio-Techne to Host Conference Call on November 5, 2025, to Announce First Quarter Fiscal 2026 Financial Results
summary: Bio-Techne Corporation (NASDAQ: TECH) today announced that management will host a conference call and webcast on Wednesday, November 5, 2025, at 8:00 a.m. CST to review its first quarter fiscal 2026 financial results.
